PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1997-883 of July 3, 1997 which will extend the term of appointment of DAVID ZIMMER as a full-time member of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Toronto Regional Office) until June 9, 2003; and designation of DAVID ZIMMER as Assistant Deputy Chairperson of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Toronto Regional Office); effective June 10, 1998.
